name: Christopher_Knight_Home_Guernsey_Studded_Faux_Leather_Storage_Ottoman_Bench
description:
Keep toys out of sight when not in use with this sleek storage ottoman. The ottoman features a padded seat, studded accents, and a long rectangular design, which allows it to serve as a great seating option when guests come to visit. The top lifts up, so you can toss toys in for quick and easy clean-up when you need it.
